{"tid":262161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行山失蹤青年伏屍山邊】警列謀殺　重案拘3人 (11:55)","createTime":"2017-05-29T04:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T04:20:01.000Z","uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3babf81ebe4aebb460100ab7917cb1d4d3f86e72","tid":262161,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T04:19:12.000Z","msg":"20歲青年郭葦諾（Bosco）昨凌晨離開將軍澳寓所，與3名朋友到區內行夜山，其間接聽電話後獨自下山，早上8時許被發現伏屍衛奕信徑第3段近五桂山。案件交由東九龍總區重案組跟進，改列「謀殺」處理，拘捕3名涉案男子，法醫到場驗屍。<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170529/s00001/1496030012125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170529%2Fs00001%2F1496030012125&d=ILV6eVzZah1BYd98yfVyj7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=30b774a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170529%2Fs00001%2F1496030012125&h=d1bbd920\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170529/s00001/1496030012125</a>"},{"pid":"bd890b75b5510b0643cf8627dbd10c8e70267947","tid":262161,"uid":19463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T04:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}